Get cash back rewards for your everyday purchases.

The best cash back credit cards are designed with your spending habits in mind. Capital One cash rewards cards offer cash back benefits that reward you for the purchases youre already making. Whether youd like to earn more cash back on dining and entertainment with the Savor card, or earn a flat rate on all your everyday purchaseslike gas and retailyou can find a Capital One card that fits your needs. Every Capital One cash back credit card gives you a percentage back for all qualifying purchasesso you can get rewarded for every dollar you spend.

Cash back credit card FAQs

Which Capital One cash back card is right for me?

Which cash back card is best for you depends entirely on which rewards are most important to you. Start by looking at the reward percentage categories for each card and how they align with your overall spending habits. 1  

  • The Capital One QuicksilverOne card offers 1.5% cash back on all of your everyday purchases.
  • The Capital One Quicksilver card offers 1.5% cash back on all of your everyday purchases
  • The Capital One SavorOne card offers unlimited 3% cash back on dining, entertainment, popular streaming services, and grocery stores.
  • The Capital One Savor card offers unlimited 4% cash back on dining, entertainment & popular streaming services, and 3% at grocery stores. 

How do cash back credit cards work?

A cash back credit card allows you to earn cash back on your purchases. Typically, you earn a certain percentage of cash back on your overall spending. With some cards, you may earn more for certain spending categories.

  • Cards under the Savor card suite offer higher cash-back incentives across dining and entertainment categories.
  • Cards under the Quicksilver card suite offer a flat-rate cash back percentage for all of your everyday purchases. 

Can I redeem my rewards for something other than cash back?

Yes, cash back cards can be redeemed for a number of rewards.

  • Cards under both the Quicksilver card suite and Savor card suite can be redeemed for cash back on other rewards such as entertainment and travel.
  • All of these Capital One cash back card options can also be redeemed for gift cards and eligible purchases on both PayPal and Amazon.

Is there a limit to the amount of cash back rewards I can earn with my Capital One card?

There is no cap to the amount of rewards you can earn on purchases made with your Capital One cash back card.

  • The Quicksilver card suite offers unlimited rewards for all of your everyday purchases.
  • The Savor card suite offers unlimited rewards in dining and entertainment categories, as well as everyday purchases. 

Do Capital One cash back cards have an annual fee?

Both the Quicksilver suite and Savor suite offer Capital One cash back credit card options with no annual fees. Compare Capital One cash back credit cards using this comparison tool.

Do Capital One cash back rewards expire?

Rewards earned with a Capital One cash back rewards card dont expire as long as your account is open, and theres no limit to the amount of rewards you can earn.

How do I redeem my cash back rewards?

If youre already a Capital One cash back card customer, you can redeem your cash back by signing in to your account.
